{"type": "article", "id": 14648, "title": "储物柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-09T07:27:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000315nwqbO0E3voJQgxL4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自南非的设计搭档 Byron 和 Gomez 设计了这款储物柜并获得了今年的 Allan Peters Award。储物柜由大大小小形状不一的方形抽屉组成，打开时错落有致。每一个抽屉的表面都是带年轮的木纹，三条显著的白线将纹路断开，组成了不规则也不凌乱的构图。中心的白色的凹槽则帮助人们打开抽屉，但正面却完全看不出来，非常巧妙。储物柜的构造本有些像中国古代的药柜，但充满艺术感的外形也赋予了这款柜子优雅和现代。<a href=\"http://www.byronandgomez.co.uk/work/#/log-stackcabinet/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142111ZHnLw56z20WOIiS1.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"397\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261421116edmkp5gRZhvGTFK.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"494\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65866667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261421128c4ySszPNvj7bIoC.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"395\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}